CustomField.description: This field is automatically populated with the status of the job run, such as Log (indicating successful execution with logged details) or Error (indicating a failure). Use this status for reporting to monitor job outcomes and identify issues. Do not modify this field, as it is system-generated and essential for accurate reporting.
